{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01W9CLkr9HqaEarze5DeMrDQ","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information I need. Let me compile the complete findings:\n\n## Exploration Complete\n\nI've gathered all the necessary information for creating a new ReferralPage component and route. Here's the full breakdown:\n\n---\n\n## 1. **App.tsx Route Configuration** \n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx`\n\nRoutes are defined within `<Routes>` inside the `AppContent()` component (lines 370–388). Each game/page route is wrapped with `<RouteErrorBoundary>` for error isolation:\n\n```tsx\n<Route path=\"/profile\" element={<RouteErrorBoundary label=\"Profile\"><ProfilePage /></RouteErrorBoundary>} />\n<Route path=\"/loot\" element={<RouteErrorBoundary label=\"Loot\"><LootPage /></RouteErrorBoundary>} />\n<Route path=\"/quests\" element={<RouteErrorBoundary label=\"Quests\"><QuestsPage /></RouteErrorBoundary>} />\n<Route path=\"/fairness\" element={<RouteErrorBoundary label=\"Fairness\"><FairnessPage /></RouteErrorBoundary>} />\n```\n\n**Pattern to follow**: Add `<Route path=\"/referrals\" element={<RouteErrorBoundary label=\"Referrals\"><ReferralPage /></RouteErrorBoundary>} />` before the catch-all `*` route.\n\n---\n\n## 2. **RouteErrorBoundary Component**\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/components/RouteErrorBoundary.tsx` (full file, lines 1–52)\n\n```tsx\nimport { Component, type ReactNode, type ErrorInfo } from \"react\";\n\ninterface Props {\n  children: ReactNode;\n  /** Shown in the error UI so the player knows which area broke. */\n  label?: string;\n}\n\ninterface State {\n  hasError: boolean;\n  error: Error | null;\n}\n\n/**\n * Per-route error boundary — catches render crashes in a single feature\n * without tearing down the whole app (sidebar, header, other games stay alive).\n */\nexport class RouteErrorBoundary extends Component<Props, State> {\n  constructor(props: Props) {\n    super(props);\n    this.state = { hasError: false, error: null };\n  }\n\n  static getDerivedStateFromError(error: Error): Partial<State> {\n    return { hasError: true, error };\n  }\n\n  componentDidCatch(error: Error, info: ErrorInfo): void {\n    console.error(`[RouteErrorBoundary${this.props.label ? ` — ${this.props.label}` : \"\"}]`, error, info);\n  }\n\n  render() {\n    if (!this.state.hasError) return this.props.children;\n\n    return (\n      <div className=\"route-error\">\n        <h2 className=\"route-error__title\">Something went wrong</h2>\n        {this.props.label && (\n          <p className=\"route-error__label\">{this.props.label} hit an error.</p>\n        )}\n        <pre className=\"route-error__detail\">{this.state.error?.message}</pre>\n        <button\n          type=\"button\"\n          className=\"route-error__retry\"\n          onClick={() => this.setState({ hasError: false, error: null })}\n        >\n          Try Again\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    );\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. **Sidebar.tsx — Referrals NavLink**\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/components/Sidebar.tsx` (lines 162–171)\n\n**Confirmed**: The Referrals NavLink is already present from iteration 21:\n\n```tsx\n<NavLink to=\"/referrals\" className={({ isActive }) => `nv-item ${isActive ? \"active\" : \"\"}`} style={{ \"--nc\": \"var(--color-green)\" } as React.CSSProperties}>\n  <div className=\"nv-ico\">\n    <svg viewBox=\"0 0 17 17\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\">\n      <path d=\"M7 3.5H4C3.2 3.5 2.5 4.2 2.5 5V12C2.5 12.8 3.2 13.5 4 13.5H13C13.8 13.5 14.5 12.8 14.5 12V9.5\" />\n      <path d=\"M10 2L14.5 2L14.5 6.5\" />\n      <line x1=\"14.5\" y1=\"2\" x2=\"8\" y2=\"8.5\" />\n    </svg>\n  </div>\n  <span className=\"nv-lbl\">Referrals</span>\n</NavLink>\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. **Existing Referral Feature Structure**\n**Directory**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/`\n\nCurrent structure:\n- `index.ts` — exports `useReferralApply` hook\n- `hooks/useReferralApply.ts` — auto-applies stored referral code on auth\n\n**Needs to be added**: `ReferralPage.tsx` and supporting components.\n\n---\n\n## 5. **Authentication Pattern — useSession & useWallet**\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/context/SessionContext.tsx` (lines 1–79)\n\n**SessionContext** provides:\n```tsx\ninterface SessionContextValue {\n  isAuthenticated: boolean;\n  isAuthenticating: boolean;\n  accessToken: string | null;\n  authenticate: () => Promise<string>;\n  clearSession: () => void;\n}\n\nexport function useSession() {\n  // Returns { isAuthenticated, isAuthenticating, accessToken, authenticate, clearSession }\n}\n```\n\n**useWallet** from `@rng-utopia/wallet/hooks`:\n```tsx\nconst { connected, address } = useWallet();\n```\n\n---\n\n## 6. **Unauthenticated State Pattern — LootPage Example**\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/LootPage.tsx` (full file, lines 1–44)\n\n```tsx\nimport { usePlayerProfile } from \"../features/player-profile\";\nimport { ProfileLoot } from \"../features/player-profile/components/ProfileLoot\";\n\nexport function LootPage() {\n  const { myProfile, loading } = usePlayerProfile();\n\n  if (loading) {\n    return (\n      <div className=\"loot-page\">\n        <div className=\"loot-page__loading\">Loading...</div>\n      </div>\n    );\n  }\n\n  if (!myProfile) {\n    return (\n      <div className=\"loot-page\">\n        <div className=\"loot-page__connect\">\n          <h2>Connect Wallet</h2>\n          <p>Connect your wallet to view your loot.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    );\n  }\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"loot-page\">\n      <div className=\"loot-page__header\">\n        <h1 className=\"loot-page__title\">Loot</h1>\n        <p className=\"loot-page__subtitle\">\n          Open crates and claim your rewards\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"loot-page__content\">\n        <ProfileLoot profile={myProfile} />\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 7. **Referral API Functions**\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/lib/referral-api.ts` (full file, lines 1–161)\n\nKey response types and functions available:\n\n```tsx\nexport interface ReferralStatsResponse {\n  referredCount: number;\n  activeCount: number;\n  totalVolumeLamports: string;\n  totalEarnedLamports: string;\n  pendingLamports: string;\n}\n\nexport interface ReferralEarningItem {\n  roundId: string;\n  gameType: string;\n  refereeWallet: string;\n  wagerLamports: string;\n  earnedLamports: string;\n  createdAt: string;\n}\n\nexport interface ReferralEarningsResponse {\n  items: ReferralEarningItem[];\n  pagination: { page: number; totalPages: number };\n}\n\nexport async function getReferralCode(token: string): Promise<ReferralCodeResponse>\nexport async function setReferralCode(token: string, code: string): Promise<ReferralCodeResponse>\nexport async function getReferralStats(token: string): Promise<ReferralStatsResponse>\nexport async function getReferralEarnings(token: string, page?: number, limit?: number): Promise<ReferralEarningsResponse>\nexport async function requestReferralClaim(token: string): Promise<ClaimResponse>\nexport async function pollClaimStatus(token: string, claimId: string): Promise<ClaimResponse>\n```\n\n---\n\n## 8. **Referral Code Capture & Auto-Apply Flow**\n**App.tsx lines 455–464**:\n\n```tsx\nfunction ReferralCapture() {\n  const { code } = useParams<{ code: string }>();\n  if (code) {\n    try {\n      localStorage.setItem(\"referral_code\", JSON.stringify({ code, capturedAt: new Date().toISOString() }));\n    } catch {\n      // localStorage may be unavailable (private browsing, storage full) — proceed with redirect\n    }\n  }\n  return <Navigate to=\"/\" replace />;\n}\n```\n\nRoute: `/r/:code` (line 386)\n\n**Auto-apply hook** (`useReferralApply`) is called in `AppContent()` (line 349) and runs on auth to apply the stored code.\n\n---\n\n## Summary of Files\n\n### Read-Only Access (You have full visibility):\n1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx` — Route definitions, HomePage, ReferralCapture, NotFoundPage\n2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/components/RouteErrorBoundary.tsx` — Error boundary component\n3. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/components/Sidebar.tsx` — Referrals NavLink already present\n4. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/context/SessionContext.tsx` — Auth context\n5. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/lib/referral-api.ts` — Referral backend API\n6. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/referral/hooks/useReferralApply.ts` — Auto-apply hook\n7. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/LootPage.tsx` — Example of unauthenticated state pattern\n8. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/ProfilePage.tsx` — Example of auth-gated page\n\n### To Create (within referral feature):\n- `ReferralPage.tsx` — Main page component\n- Supporting component(s) for stats, code display, copy functionality, earnings list, claim button, etc."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a576d06dc5c852525 (use SendMessage with to: 'a576d06dc5c852525' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 66244\ntool_uses: 24\nduration_ms: 73335</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cad61997-ae30-4665-891e-0380cf7cb6d1","uuid":"95f125a3-e09b-4c72-bbca-c85919de7c7f","timestamp":"2026-03-25T13:12:10.313Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"I need to create a new ReferralPage component and route in the platform